## ğŸ“Œ **2ï¸âƒ£ Basic Usage**

```bash
# Start live capture (default):
sudo tcpdump

# Show all available interfaces:
sudo tcpdump -D

# Capture on specific interface (e.g., ens33):
sudo tcpdump -i ens33
```

